PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Transport of Robert Pace, of Halifax, Nova Scotia, as a director of the Board of Directors of the Canadian National Railway Company to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of George T.H. Cooper, whose term has expired.
